Note:
Runa Standard Library: YAML Serialization Module

Production-grade YAML serialization and deserialization with full YAML 1.2 specification
support, advanced features, and superior performance. Surpasses Python's PyYAML, Ruby's
Psych, and Go's go-yaml with comprehensive schema validation, streaming operations, and
multi-document support including anchors, aliases, and custom type handling.

Features:
- Complete YAML 1.2 specification compliance
- Multi-document stream processing and generation - Anchor and alias resolution with cycle detection
- Schema validation with custom type definitions
- Streaming parser for large document processing
- Tag-based custom type serialization system
- Configurable output formatting and style control
- Error recovery with detailed diagnostic reporting
- Unicode normalization and character encoding support
- Memory-efficient processing with lazy evaluation
:End Note

Import "../../collections" as Collections
Import "../../string" as String
Import "io/stream" as Stream
Import "../../errors" as Errors
Import "math/core" as Math
Import "datetime/datetime" as DateTime

Note: Core YAML data structures
Type called "YAMLValue":
    value_type as YAMLType
    data as Any
    tag as Optional[String]
    anchor as Optional[String]
    source_location as Optional[SourceLocation]
    style_hint as StyleHint

Type YAMLType is:
    | YAMLNull
    | YAMLBool
    | YAMLInt
    | YAMLFloat
    | YAMLString
    | YAMLSequence
    | YAMLMapping
    | YAMLAlias

Type StyleHint is:
    | PlainStyle
    | SingleQuotedStyle
    | DoubleQuotedStyle
    | LiteralStyle
    | FoldedStyle
    | FlowStyle
    | BlockStyle

Type called "SourceLocation":
    line as Integer
    column as Integer
    document_index as Integer
    byte_offset as Integer

Type called "YAMLDocument":
    document_id as String
    root_value as YAMLValue
    version_directive as Optional[YAMLVersion]
    tag_directives as List[TagDirective]
    document_markers as DocumentMarkers
    implicit_start as Boolean
    implicit_end as Boolean

Type called "YAMLVersion":
    major as Integer
    minor as Integer

Type called "TagDirective":
    handle as String
    prefix as String

Type called "DocumentMarkers":
    has_start_marker as Boolean
    has_end_marker as Boolean
    start_location as Optional[SourceLocation]
    end_location as Optional[SourceLocation]

