    character_offset as 0
    document_index as 0

Process called "create_default_parsing_options" returns ParsingOptions:
    Return ParsingOptions with:
    yaml_version as YAMLVersion with major as 1 and minor as 2
    allow_unicode as true
    allow_duplicate_keys as false
    preserve_quotes as false
    max_aliases as 100
    max_depth as 100
