    Return ""

Process called "get_current_scanner_location" that takes scanner as YAMLScanner returns SourceLocation:
    Return SourceLocation with:
    line as 1
    column as 1
    document_index as 0
    byte_offset as 0

Process called "check_document_start" that takes scanner as YAMLScanner returns Boolean:
    Note: Implementation would check for "---" document start marker
    Return false

Process called "check_document_end" that takes scanner as YAMLScanner returns Boolean:
    Note: Implementation would check for "..." document end marker Return false

Process called "scan_directive" that takes scanner as YAMLScanner returns YAMLToken:
    Note: Implementation would scan YAML directives like %YAML and %TAG
    Return create_token with type as StreamEnd and value as "" and location as get_current_scanner_location with scanner as scanner

Process called "scan_block_entry" that takes scanner as YAMLScanner returns YAMLToken:
