Note: Placeholder implementations for complex operations
Process called "determine_block_end_event" that takes token as YAMLToken returns YAMLEvent:
    Return YAMLEvent with event_type as SequenceEndEvent and location as token.location

Process called "resolve_scalar_tag" that takes resolver as YAMLResolver and value as String and implicit as Boolean returns String:
    If implicit:
    Return resolve_implicit_tag with resolver as resolver and value as value
    Otherwise:
    Return "tag:yaml.org,2002:str"

Process called "resolve_implicit_tag" that takes resolver as YAMLResolver and value as String returns String:
    If value is equal to "null" or value is equal to "~" or value is equal to "":
    Return "tag:yaml.org,2002:null"
    Else if value is equal to "true" or value is equal to "false":
    Return "tag:yaml.org,2002:bool"
    Else if is_integer_string with str as value:
    Return "tag:yaml.org,2002:int"
    Else if is_float_string with str as value:
    Return "tag:yaml.org,2002:float"
    Otherwise:
    Return "tag:yaml.org,2002:str"

Process called "is_integer_string" that takes str as String returns Boolean:
    Try:
    Let parsed_int be Math.parse_integer with integer_string as str
    Return true
    Catch conversion_error:
    Return false

Process called "is_float_string" that takes str as String returns Boolean:
    Try:
    Let parsed_float be Math.parse_float with float_string as str
    Return true
    Catch conversion_error:
    Return false

Process called "determine_yaml_type_from_tag" that takes tag as String returns YAMLType:
    Match tag:
    When "tag:yaml.org,2002:null":
    Return YAMLNull
    When "tag:yaml.org,2002:bool":
    Return YAMLBool
    When "tag:yaml.org,2002:int":
    Return YAMLInt
    When "tag:yaml.org,2002:float":
    Return YAMLFloat
    When "tag:yaml.org,2002:str":
    Return YAMLString
    When "tag:yaml.org,2002:seq":
    Return YAMLSequence
    When "tag:yaml.org,2002:map":
    Return YAMLMapping
    Otherwise:
    Return YAMLString

Process called "construct_scalar_value" that takes value as String and tag as String returns Any:
    Match tag:
    When "tag:yaml.org,2002:null":
    Return null
    When "tag:yaml.org,2002:bool":
    Return value is equal to "true"
    When "tag:yaml.org,2002:int":
    Return Math.parse_integer with integer_string as value
    When "tag:yaml.org,2002:float":
    Return Math.parse_float with float_string as value
    Otherwise:
    Return value

Process called "find_constructor" that takes loader as YAMLLoader and tag as String returns Optional[Constructor]:
    If Collections.Dict.contains_key with dict as loader.constructors and key as tag:
    Return loader.constructors[tag]
    Otherwise:
    Return None

Process called "construct_default_value" that takes loader as YAMLLoader and node as YAMLValue returns YAMLValue:
    Return node

Process called "represent_with_default_representer" that takes representer as YAMLRepresenter and data as Any returns YAMLValue:
    Return convert_runa_value_to_yaml_value with runa_value as data

Process called "get_data_type_name" that takes data as Any returns String:
    If data is null:
    Return "NullType"
    Else if data is Boolean:
    Return "Boolean"
    Else if data is Integer:
    Return "Integer"
    Else if data is Float:
    Return "Float"
    Else if data is String:
    Return "String"
    Else if data is List:
    Return "List"
    Else if data is Dictionary:
    Return "Dictionary"
    Otherwise:
    Return "UnknownType"

